-- Chevron says 220,000 bpd Pembroke refinery fully operational
-- 
-- Fri Jun 3, 2011 3:50am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/03/us-chevron-refinery-operations-idUSTRE7521DC20110603

 

 SINGAPORE  (Reuters) - Chevron Corp ( CVX.N ) said its 220,000 barrels per day (bpd) Pembroke refinery in southwest Wales was operating on Friday. 

 "The refinery is fully operational," Chevron said in a statement e-mailed to Reuters. Four people were killed and one was seriously injured in an explosion at the plant on Thursday. (Reporting by  Simon Webb ; Editing by Himani Sarkar)